title: #129 - Max Stirner
description: This week Dan is partially handicapped by a case of the flu, but that's not going to stop your hosts from discussing the nihilistic egoism of Max Stirner. He's a relatively unknown philosopher who's looking out for number one and not afraid to say it. He's also a meme, which is...weird. Also discussed this week: Force Awakens reviews, Elon Musk is a weirdo, and more!
